  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;for support of the BCcampus Open Textbook Project program&quot;</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;Created and funded by the British Columbia Ministry of Advanced Education, BCcampus is an organization that provides teaching, learning, educational technology, and OER support to British Columbia&#x2019;s postsecondary system. BCcampus will manage the large Open Textbook Project; work to increase the number of faculty and instructors using open textbooks in British Columbia institutions and other jurisdictions; and build capacity, advocacy, and knowledge of OER in the B.C. system. This project will promote greater mainstream adoption of open textbooks in higher education. &quot;</narrative>
  </description>
